      "body" : "\"addnode IP remove\" with 0.8.2 QT returns \"Error: Node has not been added. (code -24)\" unless node was added using \"addnode IP add\" command previously and that is true even for nodes that were connected the usual way prior to using \"addnode IP remove\". In other words, if node X is already connected, one still must use \"addnode X add\" and then \"addnode X remove\" to remove node X (it is not actualy removed, as posted earlier by randy-waterhouse and wtogami).",
